title: Brand New Apartments Opening this Fall - LEASING NOW!
posting_body: ['Studios starting at $1199!', ' Prelease and reserve your brand new home today!', 'CLARA APARTMENTS offers 78 new apartment homes in the University District, steps away from UW and the “Ave.”', 'Studios, one- and two-bedrooms available.', 'Secured building with thoughtfully designed layouts and high-end finishes.', 'Features:', '- Private kitchens', '- Rooftop deck', '- Indoor bike storage', '- Storage spaces for rent', '- Community lounge with TV and kitchen', '- Study lounge', '- Courtyard', '- Package delivery lockers', 'Opening in time for FALL QUARTER: students, inquire with us about reserving your unit TODAY!', '*This is a student-only community*', 'Apply and find criteria here: <URL>', 'Prices, plans, specifications, terms, incentives, advertising, and availability are subject to change without notice.', 'Floor plans and photos are for illustrative purposes only.']
